1048  a small deflection theory for curved sandwich plates   stein,m and mayers,j  naca r1008, 1951  a small deflection theory for curved sandwich plates    a smalldeflection theory that takes into account deformations due to transverse shear is presented for the elasticbehavior analysis of orthotropic plates of constant cylindrical curvature with considerations of buckling included   the theory is applicable primarily to sandwich construction  
